Package game_physics

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CollisionBox
    The CollisionBox represents the area around the Sprite2D or other game object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CoCircle
    The class CoCircle represents the circle type of CollisionBox.This is good solution for the circle images.It represents the circle around the sprite.
    CollisionUtility
    This is utility class for collision.It contains methods for collision functionalities.
    CoMesh
    The class CoMesh represents the mesh type of CollisionBox.
    CoRectangle
    The class CoRectangle represents the rectangle type of CollisionBox.This is the simplest and most used type of collision box.
    Vector2
    This class represent 2 dimensional Vector who have two components x and y.
